quran[25]{c,v,t,f}:
  69,52,"Ee ku tasbiixso, xurmo weynee, oo huf Magaca Rabbigaa (Allaah), Weynaha, Sharafta Badan.",1:[Subxaannallaah wa bi xamdihi Subxaanallaahi Cadiim).]
  74,31,"Kama aanu yeelin waardiyada Naarta waxaan ahayn malaa'ig, umana aanu yeelin tiradooda waxaan ahayn imtixaan ahaan gaalada - si ay ehlu Kitaabku u yaqiinsadaan (Xaq ahaanta Islaamka), mu’miniintuna u kororsadaan Iimaan - oo aanay kuwaa ehlu Kitaabka ah iyo mu’miniinta u shakiyin, iyo in kuwaa uu quluubtoodu ku jiro cudur iyo gaalada (mushrikiinta ah) u yidhaahdaan: Muxuu Alle ugala jeedaa tusaalahan? Sidaasuu Alle u lumiyaa qofkuu doono, oo u hanuuniyaa qofkuu doono. Ma jiro wax og ciidammada (Alle) Rabbigaa Isaga maahee. Waxan la soo sheegayna ma aha waxaan aheyn waano ku socota dadka."
  74,32,"Mayee, waxaan ku dhaartay dayaxa,"
  74,33,"Iyo habeenka markuu tago."
  75,28,"Oo yaqiinsado inay tahay (waqtigii) tagidda (geerida)."
  75,29,"Oo lagu isku maro labada jeeni (kafno)."
  75,30,"Waa xagga Rabbigaa Maalintaas halka laysu wadaa."
  76,22,"Hubaal kani waa abaalgud aad leedihiin, dadaalkiinniina waa la idiin gudi oo ajar weyn la idinka siin."
  76,23,"Annagaa kugu soo dejinnay Qur’aanka (Nabi Muxammadow) si qayb qayb ah (Suurado iyo Aayado) soo dejin dhan."
  76,24,"Ee ku samir Xukunka Rabbigaa, hana adeecin denbiile iyo abaal darne midna."
  77,19,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  77,20,"Miyaanaan idinka abuurin biyo daciif ah liita?"
  77,21,"Markaas yeelnay meel aamin ah gudaheed (riximka),"
  78,16,"Iyo beero isku maran."
  78,17,"Maalinka kala baxu (Qiyaamaha) waa waqti go’an."
  78,18,"Maalinka marka Buunka la afuufi, oo aad iman idinkoo ummado kala duwan ah;"
  79,10,"Waxay (haatan) leeyihiin: Ma waxaa naloo soo celin (dhimashadayada kaddib) sidayadii hore (ee nolosha adduunka)?"
  79,11,"Ma markaan noqonno lafo bololay?"
  79,12,"Waxay odhan: Taasi waa noqosho khasaaro ah."
  80,7,"Eedna kaama saarna hadduusan hanuunin oo daahirin naftiisa,"
  80,8,"Kan se kuu yimid isagoo dadaalaya,"
  80,9,"Oo (Alle ka) baqa,"
  81,4,"Oo geela rimman (qofka waxa uu maal ugu jecel yahay) uu cidleeyo (isaga tago oo laga hayaamo)."
  81,5,"Dugaagga la soo wada kulmiyo (qisaas darteed)."
  81,6,"Badaha la shido (ama isku soo fatahmaan);"
